<span id="freeTextContainer3756006909521905768">What a perfect title! Despite knowing nothing about sailing this book took me on a journeys around the world which I would never make (even with today&apos;s technology). It also takes the reader on personal journeys, exploring why decisions are made and touching on the impact those decisions have on not just the individual making the decision but on others in their lives. For me it confirmed that, to succeed at this level and particularly in sport, you have to be not only incredibly driven but also </span>
  <span id="freeText3756006909521905768" style="display:none">What a perfect title! Despite knowing nothing about sailing this book took me on a journeys around the world which I would never make (even with today's technology). It also takes the reader on personal journeys, exploring why decisions are made and touching on the impact those decisions have on not just the individual making the decision but on others in their lives. For me it confirmed that, to succeed at this level and particularly in sport, you have to be not only incredibly driven but also selfish. <br />A glimpse into a fascinating time in history.</span>
